#### **CTA Placement Strategy:**
1. **Mid-Article CTA** (after problem/benefit section): Soft introduction to app
2. **End-Article CTA** (final call): Strong conversion push with urgency
3. **Sidebar CTA** (optional): Persistent visibility during scroll

#### **App Store Badge Requirements:**
- Always include BOTH App Store + Google Play badges
- Use official store badges (not custom designs)
- Include "Download on" + "Get it on" official text
- Link directly to app store pages with UTM tracking

